{"body": "As I remember `join` faster then `+` (for some languages is preferable like JavaScript)\r\n\r\n```shell\r\n1.9.3p448 :006 > Benchmark.measure {  100000.times { ['aaaaaaaaa', 'bbbbbbbb', 'cccccccccc', 'eeeeeeeeee', 'ddddddddddd'].join } }\r\n =>   0.330000   0.000000   0.330000 (  0.338818)\r\n```\r\n\r\n```shell\r\n1.9.3p448 :004 > Benchmark.measure {  100000.times { 'aaaaaaaaa' + 'bbbbbbbb' + 'cccccccccc' + 'eeeeeeeeee' + 'ddddddddddd' } }\r\n =>   0.430000   0.000000   0.430000 (  0.435451)\r\n```\r\n\r\n__P.S.__ but this line I found because of `separator` can be `nil`, and will raise exception on `+`.", "url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/comments/21584925", "created_at": "2013-07-25T21:10:40Z", "html_url": "https://github.com/rails/rails/pull/11603#issuecomment-21584925", "updated_at": "2013-07-25T21:11:13Z", "repo": "rails", "issue_id": 11603, "user": {"following_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/following{/other_user}", "events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/events{/privacy}", "organizations_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/orgs", "url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg", "gists_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/gists{/gist_id}", "html_url": "https://github.com/pftg", "subscriptions_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/subscriptions", "avatar_url": "https://2.gravatar.com/avatar/712a9cc852c438c0873ef0a98f749f2e?d=https%3A%2F%2Fidenticons.github.com%2F58adcd3cfec4758f40b142a29c054d55.png", "repos_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/repos", "received_events_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/received_events", "gravatar_id": "712a9cc852c438c0873ef0a98f749f2e", "starred_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/starred{/owner}{/repo}", "login": "pftg", "type": "User", "id": 125715, "followers_url": "https://api.github.com/users/pftg/followers"}, "owner": "rails", "_id": {"$oid": "5237d2c6bd3543c151007ec2"}, "id": 21584925, "issue_url": "https://api.github.com/repos/rails/rails/issues/11